{"tid":727511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：不會將２３條立法束之高閣","createTime":"2018-07-03T05:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T03:07:11.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a06e3c12eca65cd279efd3ac572bfc6aa75a816c","tid":727511,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/lam_Y9yiD_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flam_Y9yiD_1200x0.png&h=98f1b9ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN280703519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Deditorchoice%26newsid%3DETN280703519&d=Nyti4CReHsaybVxJJYr7HMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=4ad98071\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN280703519</a><br />\n<br />\n《經濟通通訊社３日專訊》今屆政府上任一年來，親北京及建制派人士多次提出應盡早展開《基本法》２３條立法，對此特首林鄭月娥日前接受《信報》等傳媒訪問時表示，本港就國家安全立法屬憲制責任，身為特首不可推卸；她不會將２３條立法工作束之高閣，但目前仍要在社會不斷創造有利的條件，而中央亦有給予空間。<br />\n<br />\n　　她在七一回歸酒會上致詞時強調，過去一年，政府堅持「一國」之本，在大是大非上，態度絕不含糊，對觸碰國家底線的行為絕不容忍；同時善用「兩制」之利，在中央大力支持下，積極參與「一帶一路」建設和「粵港澳大灣區」發展。<br />\n<br />\n　　被問到香港青年人對國家認同感淡薄，她指上任一年以來，青年人的不滿「肯定無惡劣咗」，而青年工作必須保持耐心。（ｃｌ）"},{"pid":"6f87e1d3c771783ce9d03a30d5d744dba9b30137","tid":727511,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:17:35.000Z","msg":"邱吉爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e026059fc722ff5549183eb5333efc68af9c11c","tid":727511,"uid":1441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"其實佢